[Method]
Arrange
[Prefix]
dcl_ListView_
[Desc]
This method will format the layout of all the items in the ListView control. \par
\par \pard\fi-1100\li1100 0   \b Left\b0 \tab Aligns items along the left edge of the ListView
\par \pard\fi-1100\li1100 1   \b Top\b0 \tab Aligns items along the top edge of the ListView
\par \pard\fi-1100\li1100 2   \b Default\b0 \tab Aligns items according to the ListView\rquote s current alignment styles (the default value).
\par \pard\fi-1100\li1100 3   \b GridSnap\b0 \tab Snaps all icons to the nearest grid position 
\par \pard\fi-0\li0
[Arguments]
<CONTROL>
\par\tab nStyle
[as Integer]


