[Method]
GetItemText
[Prefix]
dcl_ListView_
[Desc]
This method will return the text of an item in a ListView control. If a ListView with a Report style is called the optional \cf1 nColIndex \cf0 may need to be used, otherwise it's not required for any other style of ListView.
[Arguments Return] as String
<CONTROL>
\par\tab nRowIndex
[as Integer]
\par\tab\i{Optional} \i0 nColIndex 
[as Integer]


[Method]
GetRowItems
[Prefix]
dcl_ListView_
[Desc]
This method will return a list containing the text of a specified row in a ListView control. This method is useful for ListView controls with the Report style set.
[Arguments Return] as List of Strings
<CONTROL>
\par\tab nRowIndex
[as Integer]


[Method]
GetColumnItems
