This method will set the text of an item in a ListView control. If a ListView with a Report style is called the optional \cf1 nColIndex \cf0 may need to be used, otherwise it's not required for any other style of ListView.
[Arguments]
<CONTROL>
\par\tab NewText
[as String]
\par\tab nRowIndex
[as Integer]
\par\tab\i{Optional} \i0 nColIndex 
