[Method]
GetItemImage
[Prefix]
dcl_ListView_
[Desc]
This method will retrieve the image of an item in a ListView control. If a ListView with a Report style is called the optional \cf1 nColIndex \cf0 may need to be used, otherwise it's not required for any other style of ListView. This method is not available for the BlockList control.
[Arguments Return] as Integer
<CONTROL>
\par\tab nRowIndex 
[as Integer]
\par\tab\i{Optional} \i0 nColIndex
[as Integer]


